NAME

DateTime::Locale::zu_ZA - Locale data examples for the Zulu South Africa (zu-ZA) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Zulu South Africa locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ULwesibili, Februwari 5, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ULwesihlanu, Disemba 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = UMgqibelo, Septhemba 15, -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Februwari 5, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Disemba 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Septhemba 15, -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Feb 5, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Dis 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sep 15, -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2/5/08
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 12/22/95
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 9/15/-10
